# @imqueue — Commercial license & support

> Commercial licensing and paid support for @imqueue, an RPC framework over an inter-communication messaging queue for Node.js & TypeScript microservices. The framework is open source under GPL-3.0; a commercial license lets you ship it inside a closed-source product without the GPL source-release obligation.

The open-source packages (@imqueue/core, @imqueue/rpc, @imqueue/cli) and their documentation live at https://imqueue.org. This site covers licensing and support only.

