# @imqueue

> RPC over an inter-communication messaging queue for service-oriented Node.js & TypeScript back-ends. Self-describing services generate their own strongly-typed clients — no hand-written client code, no service discovery, no load balancer.

@imqueue is an open-source framework (GPL-3.0). Core packages: @imqueue/core (reliable message queue over Redis), @imqueue/rpc (typed RPC with automatic client generation), @imqueue/cli (scaffolding and orchestration of services). Commercial licensing and support for closed-source products: https://imqueue.com

